profile:
Professional building consultant serving the Central Interior of British Columbia for over 25 years. Residential & Commercial building inspections. Additional services provided are mold and indoor air quality testing - asbestos assessment & testing - radon testing - WETT inspections for wood stoves and chimneys - water testing - exterior building envelop  & oil tank inspections, new building construction inspections, strata depreciation reports and property management.
Certified and registers with ASTTBC and licensed by Consumer Protection B.C. 
Over 15,000 inspections conducted. Experienced and knowledgeable looking out for your best interest only.
